'''约瑟夫·罗比内特·拜登三世'''（{{lang-en|Joseph Robinette Biden III}}，{{bd|1969年|2月3日|2015年|5月30日}}），通称為'''博·拜登'''（{{lang|en|Beau Biden}}）<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.latimes.com/local/obituaries/la-me-beau-biden-20150531-story.html|title = Beau Biden, son of vice president, dies at 46|last = Memoli|first = Michael A.|date = 2015-05-30|work = Los Angeles Times|accessdate = 2016-01-22|last2 = Colker|first2 = David|archive-date = 2016-01-30|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160130104900/http://www.latimes.com/local/obituaries/la-me-beau-biden-20150531-story.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>，是一位[[美国|美国]]律师、{{le|美國陸軍軍法署|Judge Advocate General's Corps, United States Army}}[[軍官|軍官]]、[[特拉华州|特拉华州]][[民主党_(美国)|民主党]]政治人物。他于2003年加入{{le|特拉华州陆军国民警卫队|Delaware Army National Guard}}，后升至[[少校|少校]]，还于2008年在[[伊拉克战争|伊拉克战争]]期间作为随军律师到战场服役一年。2007年至2015年，博·拜登任{{le|特拉华州总检察长|Attorney General of Delaware}}（司法部长），任内为减少儿童性侵犯做出诸多努力。2013年被诊断出患有[[脑癌|脑癌]]，2015年5月30日因脑癌复发逝世，享年46岁。

== 早年生活和家庭 ==
博·拜登于1969年2月3日出生于美国[[特拉华州|特拉华州]][[威尔明顿_(特拉华州)|威尔明顿]]，是[[乔·拜登|乔·拜登]]和首任妻子[[内莉亚·亨特|内莉亚·亨特]]的长子。他还有一个弟弟[[亨特·拜登|亨特]]和妹妹娜歐蜜（{{Lang|en|Naomi}}）。<ref name=":1">{{Cite news|url = http://www.nytimes.com/2015/05/31/us/politics/joseph-r-biden-iii-vice-presidents-son-beau-dies-at-46.html|title = Beau Biden, Vice President Joe Biden’s Son, Dies at 46|last = Shear|first = Michael D.|date = 2015-05-30|work = New York Times|accessdate = 2016-01-22|archive-date = 2016-01-15|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160115135616/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/05/31/us/politics/joseph-r-biden-iii-vice-presidents-son-beau-dies-at-46.html|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url = http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-05-31/beau-biden-vice-president-s-election-winning-son-dies-at-46|title = Beau Biden, VP’s Eldest Son, Succumbs to Brain Cancer|last = Arnold|first = Laurence|date = 2015-06-01|work = [[彭博新闻社|Bloomberg]]|accessdate = 2016-01-24|last2 = Keane|first2 = Angela Greiling|archive-date = 2015-12-17|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151217150851/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-05-31/beau-biden-vice-president-s-election-winning-son-dies-at-46|dead-url = no}}</ref> 1972年12月18日，乔·拜登刚成为[[美国参议院|联邦参议员]]之后六周，内莉亚带着三个孩子在一次圣诞购物途中遭遇了交通事故，驾驶的汽车被一辆卡车从侧面撞上。内莉亚和当时还是婴儿的内奥米在事故中丧生，不满四岁的博·拜登和三岁的弟弟亨特当时也在车中，身受重伤但得以幸存。<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.people.com/article/joe-biden-family-tragedies-beau-biden-death|title = Inside Vice President Joe Biden’s Family Tragedies|last = Trainor|first = Michelle Ward|date = 2015-05-31|work = People|accessdate = 2016-01-22|archive-date = 2016-01-27|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160127223652/http://www.people.com/article/joe-biden-family-tragedies-beau-biden-death|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name=":0" />

1975年，乔·拜登与[[吉尔·拜登|吉尔·雅各布斯]]相识相恋，博和亨特非常鼓励父亲再婚，劝说他迎娶吉尔，甚至问他“‘我们’什么时候结婚”。<ref name="nyt082508">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/08/25/us/politics/25wife.html|title=Jill Biden Heads Toward Life in the Spotlight|author=Seelye, Katharine Q.|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=August 24, 2008|accessdate=August 25, 2008|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081210193454/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/08/25/us/politics/25wife.html|archivedate=2008-12-10|deadurl=no}}</ref> 1977年6月，乔·拜登与吉尔结为夫妻，博和亨特很快接受了吉尔，把她当作自己的母亲，直接叫她“妈妈”（"{{Lang|en|Mom}}"），对自己的生母内莉亚则称为“妈咪”（"{{Lang|en|Mommy}}"）。<ref name=":11">{{Cite web|url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/book-party/wp/2015/06/04/from-jill-to-mom-inside-jill-bidens-relationship-with-beau-and-hunter/|title = From ‘Jill’ to ‘Mom’ — inside Jill Biden’s relationship with Beau and Hunter|accessdate = 2016-01-22|author = |date = 2015-06-04|publisher = The Washington Post|last = Lozada|first = Carlos|archive-date = 2016-01-31|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160131014752/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/book-party/wp/2015/06/04/from-jill-to-mom-inside-jill-bidens-relationship-with-beau-and-hunter/|dead-url = no}}</ref>1981年，吉尔产下一个女儿，博和亨特兄弟两人为这个同父异母的妹妹起名[[阿什莉·拜登|阿什莉]]。<ref name=":11" /><ref>{{cite web|url = http://abcnews.go.com/Politics/fullpage?id=5659057|title = Joe and Jill Welcome Ashley|publisher = [[美国广播公司|ABC]]|accessdate = 2014-02-07|archive-date = 2014-02-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140223225114/http://abcnews.go.com/Politics/fullpage?id=5659057|dead-url = no}}</ref>

2002年，博·拜登与高中招生顾问哈莉·奥莉薇尔（{{Lang|en|Hallie Olivere}}）结为夫妻，二人共同育有一女娜塔丽（{{Lang|en|Natalie}}）和一子亨特（{{Lang|en|Hunter}}）。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://heavy.com/news/2015/05/beau-biden-wife-widow-hallie-biden-joe-daughter-in-law-children-kids-photos-bio-family-funeral/|title = Hallie Biden, Beau’s Wife: 5 Fast Facts You Need to Know|accessdate = 2016-01-22|author = |date = 2015-05-31|publisher = Heavy.com|first = Tom|last = Cleary|archive-date = 2016-01-26|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160126212906/http://heavy.com/news/2015/05/beau-biden-wife-widow-hallie-biden-joe-daughter-in-law-children-kids-photos-bio-family-funeral/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="votesmart">{{cite web|url=http://www.votesmart.org/bio.php?can_id=69559|title=Attorney General Joseph Robinette 'Beau' Biden III (DE)|accessdate=August 26, 2008|publisher=votesmart.org|archive-date=2011-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110521060632/http://www.votesmart.org/bio.php?can_id=69559|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url = http://www.usatoday.com/news/religion/2008-08-25-catholic-biden_N.htm|title = Biden provides Catholic link, but renews abortion debate|accessdate = August 26, 2008|last = Banks|first = Adelle M.|date = August 24, 2008|agency = Religion News Service|work = [[USA_Today|USA Today]]|archive-date = 2008-10-14|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081014205225/http://www.usatoday.com/news/religion/2008-08-25-catholic-biden_N.htm|dead-url = no}}</ref>

==事业==
博·拜登于1987年毕业于天主教私立高中阿什米尔学院（{{Lang|en|Archmere Academy}}），这里也是他父亲乔·拜登的母校。随后进入[[宾夕法尼亚大学|宾夕法尼亚大学]]学习，1991年从这里获得学士学位。1994年，拜登从父亲曾就读的[[雪城大学法学院|雪城大学法学院]]毕业，获得[[法律博士|法律博士]]学位。<ref name=":0" /> 博·拜登曾在[[新罕布什尔州|新罕布什尔州]][[康科德_(新罕布什尔州)|康科德]]为地区法官{{Le|史蒂文·J·麥考利夫|Steven J. McAuliffe}}手下作职员。之后的1995年到2004年，博·拜登在[[美国司法部|美国司法部]]工作，最初在政策发展办公室就职，主要工作方向是{{Le|布雷迪手槍暴力防治法|Brady Handgun Violence Prevention Act}}、{{Le|防止对妇女施暴法|Violence Against Women Act}}以及失踪和被剥削儿童的相关议题；1997年至2002年，博·拜登在[[费城|费城]]任司法部下属的联邦检察官。<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite news|url = http://ncronline.org/news/people/beau-biden-oldest-son-vice-president-biden-dies-brain-cancer|title = Beau Biden, oldest son of Vice President Biden, dies of brain cancer|last = |first = |date = 2015-06-02|work = National Catholic Reporter|accessdate = 2016-01-24|archive-date = 2016-01-27|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160127190214/http://ncronline.org/news/people/beau-biden-oldest-son-vice-president-biden-dies-brain-cancer|dead-url = no}}</ref> 2001年，博·拜登曾作为美国政府的特派员之一，在[[科索沃|科索沃]]工作了四个月，帮助当地在[[南斯拉夫內戰|战后]]建立新的刑事司法系统。<ref name=":0" /> 2004年，博·拜登转而从事私人法律业务，成为特拉华州威尔明顿当地{{Lang|en|Bifferato Gentilotti Biden and Balick}}律师事务所的的合伙人，直至2006年当选特拉华州总检察长。<ref>{{cite web |first=Matt |last=Bittle |url=http://delaware.newszap.com/centraldelaware/137604-70/delaware-law-firm-hires-beau-biden |title=Delaware law firm hires Beau Biden |work=Delaware State News |date=January 12, 2015 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150602210427/http://delaware.newszap.com/centraldelaware/137604-70/delaware-law-firm-hires-beau-biden |archivedate=2015年6月2日 |accessdate=2016年1月25日 }}</ref> 2015年1月卸下总检察长一职后，博·拜登又立刻被威尔明顿的{{Lang|en|Grant & Eisenhofer}}律师事务所雇用。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2015/06/02/beau-biden-charmed-yet-cursed/28331197/|title = Beau Biden: A life charmed yet cursed|accessdate = 2016-01-24|author = |date = 2015-06-02|publisher = USA Today|first = Cris|last = Barrish|archive-date = 2015-12-28|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151228232205/http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2015/06/02/beau-biden-charmed-yet-cursed/28331197/|dead-url = no}}</ref>

=== 军旅生涯 ===
博·拜登于2003年加入{{Le|特拉华州陆军国民警卫队|Delaware Army National Guard}}，同时是{{le|美國陸軍軍法署|Judge Advocate General's Corps, United States Army}}的一员，之后升至[[少校|少校]]军衔。<ref name=":1" /><ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation-now/2015/11/10/delaware-national-guard-hq-named-beau-biden/75517420/|title = Delaware National Guard HQ to be named for Beau Biden|last = Starkey|first = Jonathan|date = 2015-11-10|work = [[USA_Today|USA Today]]|accessdate = 2016-01-24|archive-date = 2015-11-14|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151114072005/http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation-now/2015/11/10/delaware-national-guard-hq-named-beau-biden/75517420/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite news|url = http://articles.latimes.com/2008/oct/04/nation/na-trailbiden4|title = Biden bids farewell to Iraq-bound son|last = Finnegan|first = Michael|date = 2008-10-24|work = [[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|accessdate = 2016-01-24|archive-date = 2016-01-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160118132828/http://articles.latimes.com/2008/oct/04/nation/na-trailbiden4|dead-url = no}}</ref> 2008年10月3日，博·拜登随第261信号旅前往[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]][[布利斯堡|布利斯堡]]作短暂训练，随后被派往[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]。美军没有透露他在伊拉克期间的驻扎地点，但是表示他在军中的职责是担任随军律师、审判顾问以及执行《{{Le|统一军事司法法典|Uniform Code of Military Justice}}》的检察官。<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://edition.cnn.com/2008/POLITICS/10/03/biden.deployment/|title = Biden addresses his son's deployment ceremony|last = |first = |date = 2008-10-03|work = [[CNN|CNN]]|accessdate = 2016-01-24|archive-date = 2016-02-02|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160202181408/http://edition.cnn.com/2008/POLITICS/10/03/biden.deployment/|dead-url = no}}</ref> 此时恰逢他的父亲乔·拜登参加[[2008年美国总统选举|2008年大选]]活动，乔·拜登也在10月3日当天到出征仪式现场发表了演说。<ref name=":2" /><ref name="WP2">{{cite news|title = Biden's Son Off to Iraq|url = http://voices.washingtonpost.com/the-trail/2008/08/20/bidens_son_off_to_iraq.html|work = [[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|date = 2008-08-20|first = Shailagh|last = Murray|accessdate = 2016-01-24|archive-date = 2016-01-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160118132828/http://voices.washingtonpost.com/the-trail/2008/08/20/bidens_son_off_to_iraq.html|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url = http://blogs.abcnews.com/politicalradar/2008/10/biden-bids-fare.html|title = Biden Bids Farewell to Son's Guard Unit as They Deploy for Iraq|last = Jaffe|first = Matt|date = 2008-10-05|work = ABC News|accessdate = 2016-01-24|archive-date = 2016-02-02|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160202122552/http://blogs.abcnews.com/politicalradar/2008/10/biden-bids-fare.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>2008年11月，博·拜登所在部队结束了在布利斯堡的训练，奔赴伊拉克战场。<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://blogs.abcnews.com/politicalradar/2008/11/beau-biden-head.html|title = Beau Biden Heads to Iraq|last = Jaffe|first = Matthew|date = 2008-11-25|work = ABC News|accessdate = 2016-01-24|archive-date = 2016-02-02|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160202144747/http://blogs.abcnews.com/politicalradar/2008/11/beau-biden-head.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>

2009年1月，博·拜登获得特别休假从[[伊拉克战争|伊拉克战场]]归国，前往[[华盛顿特区|华盛顿特区]]参加了[[2009年美國總統就職典禮|总统就职典礼]]和父亲的副总统宣誓就职仪式，之后又回到伊拉克归队。<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://politicalticker.blogs.cnn.com/2009/01/16/bidens-son-leaves-iraq-for-inauguration/|title = Biden's son back from Iraq for the inauguration|last = |first = |date = 2009-01-16|work = CNN|accessdate = 2016-01-24|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131213014022/http://politicalticker.blogs.cnn.com/2009/01/16/bidens-son-leaves-iraq-for-inauguration/|archivedate = 2013-12-13|deadurl = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.delawareonline.com/article/20090115/NEWS/90115047/1006|title = Beau Biden gets D.C. duty, will attend inauguration|last = Parra|first = Esteban|date = 2009-01-15|work = The News Journal|accessdate = 2016-01-24|archive-date = 2016-01-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160118132828/http://www.delawareonline.com/article/20090115/NEWS/90115047/1006|dead-url = no}}</ref> 同年7月4日，博·拜登和所在部队一同在美军位于伊拉克的{{Le|胜利军营|Camp Victory}}获得了乔·拜登的接见。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB124671322919594625.html | title=Iraqis Say Reconciliation Is an Internal Matter | author=Chon, Gina | work=[[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]] | date=July 6, 2009 | accessdate=July 10, 2009 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090730212851/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB124671322919594625.html | archivedate=2009-07-30 | deadurl=no }}</ref> 2009年9月，博·拜登结束了在伊拉克的服役，随部队返回美国。乔·拜登也参加了欢迎仪式。<ref name="Return">{{cite news|url = http://www.armytimes.com/news/2009/09/ap_army_beau_biden_093009/|title = Vice president’s son returns from Iraq|last = Chase|first = Randall|date = 2009-10-01|work = Army Times|accessdate = 2016-01-25}}</ref><ref name=":3">{{Cite news|url = http://abcnews.go.com/Politics/vice-president-joe-biden-speaks-son-beau-bidens/story?id=8705947|title = VP Biden Welcomes Home Son's National Guard Brigade, Thanks Troops for Service|last = Travers|first = Karen|date = 2009-09-30|work = ABC News|accessdate = 2016-01-24|archive-date = 2016-01-31|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160131062427/http://abcnews.go.com/Politics/vice-president-joe-biden-speaks-son-beau-bidens/story?id=8705947|dead-url = no}}</ref> 之后他又回到特拉华州总检察长的职位上，继续之前的工作。<ref name=":3" />

博·拜登在出发前往伊拉克之前对特拉华州民众称自己在服役期间不会丢下总检察长的工作。他称自己将在这期间与特拉华州的幕僚成员联系，一同处理总检察长的相关事务。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.attorneygeneral.delaware.gov/media/releases/2008/openletter.pdf|title = Open Letter to Delawareans|accessdate = 2016-01-24|author = |date = 2008-09-29|publisher = Department of Justice, State of Delaware|format = pdf|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20101110002547/http://www.attorneygeneral.delaware.gov/media/releases/2008/openletter.pdf|archivedate = 2010-11-10|deadurl = yes|first = Joseph R., III|last = Biden}}</ref> 但他所在部队的一名成员称他在服役期间暂时搁置了总检察长的工作，专心投入到自己在伊拉克的服役任务中。<ref>{{cite news|url = http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2009/10/23/politics/washingtonpost/main5414082.shtml|title = Beau Biden Lays Low Amidst Senate Talk|newspaper = [[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|publisher = [[CBS_News|CBS News]]|date = 2009-10-23|accessdate = 2016-01-24|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20091025204518/http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2009/10/23/politics/washingtonpost/main5414082.shtml|archivedate = 2009-10-25|deadurl = yes}}</ref> 博·拜登凭借自己在伊拉克的表现获得了一枚[[銅星勳章|铜星勋章]]和一枚{{Le|功绩勋章 (美国)|Legion of Merit|功绩勋章}}。<ref>{{cite news|url = http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation-now/2015/11/10/delaware-national-guard-hq-named-beau-biden/75517420/|title = Delaware National Guard HQ to be named for Beau Biden|newspaper = USA Today|date = 2015-11-10|accessdate = 2016-01-24|deadurl = no|archive-date = 2015-11-14|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151114072005/http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation-now/2015/11/10/delaware-national-guard-hq-named-beau-biden/75517420/}}</ref> 为博·拜登授予功绩勋章的[[雷蒙德·奥迪耶诺|雷蒙德·奥迪耶诺]]是他在伊拉克服役期间的总指挥官，他在日后评价博·拜登“拥有那些只在伟大领袖人物身上才能见到的品质”。<ref>{{cite news|url = http://thehill.com/blogs/blog-briefing-room/news/244209-odierno-beau-biden-had-traits-of-greatest-leaders|title = Odierno: Beau Biden had traits of 'greatest leaders'|newspaper = The Hill|date = 2015-06-06|accessdate = 2016-01-24|deadurl = no|archive-date = 2016-01-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160118132828/http://thehill.com/blogs/blog-briefing-room/news/244209-odierno-beau-biden-had-traits-of-greatest-leaders}}</ref> 2012年6月，博·拜登的继母吉尔出版了一本儿童图书《不要忘记，上帝保佑我们的部队》（{{lang|en|''Don't Forget, God Bless Our Troops''}}），讲述博·拜登在军中服役的生活。<ref name="pol-2012">{{cite news|url = http://www.politico.com/news/stories/1012/81877.html|title = Jill Biden tiptoes into 2012 election|author = Slack, Donovan|newspaper = Politico|date = 2012-10-01|accessdate = 2016-01-25|archive-date = 2015-05-29|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150529131425/http://www.politico.com/news/stories/1012/81877.html|dead-url = no}}</ref> 博·拜登逝世后，特拉华州为他追授了该州最高的“卓越服务十字勋章”（{{Lang|en|The Conspicuous Service Cross}}），以表彰他的“英雄表现、服役期间的卓越功勋和杰出的成就。”<ref name=":4">{{cite news|url = http://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/mourners-pay-respects-beau-biden-delaware-n369831|title = Mourners Pay Respect to Beau Biden in Delaware|newspaper = [[NBC_News|NBC News]]|date = June 4, 2015|accessdate = November 20, 2015|deadurl = no|archive-date = 2016-01-26|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160126070054/http://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/mourners-pay-respects-beau-biden-delaware-n369831}}</ref>

=== 政治事业 ===
[[File:BeauBiden-DOJ2013.jpg|thumb]]新闻发布会]]
2006年，博·拜登首次参加公职竞选，参选{{le|特拉华州总检察长|Attorney General of Delaware}}（司法部长）一职。博·拜登的竞选对手是前州检察官、联邦助理检察官菲利斯·沃顿（{{Lang|en|Ferris Wharton}}）。选举中的主要议题包括两位候选人的资质，针对性侵犯、[[在线猎手|在线猎手]]、虐待老人和家庭暴力的措施等。最终博·拜登以52.5%的得票率获得胜利，并于2007年1月就任。<ref name=":6" /><ref name="CSPAN" />

当选后，博·拜登任命特拉华州前总检察长、特拉华州高级法院法官理查德·S·盖比雷恩（{{Lang|en|Richard S. Gebelein}}）作为副总检察长（司法部副部长），前联邦助理检察官理查德·G·安德鲁斯（{{Lang|en|Richard G. Andrews}}）为[[州檢察官|州检察官]]。<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.wboc.com/story/5788035/gebelein-named-as-delawares-next-chief-deputy-attorney-general|title = Gebelein Named as Delaware's Next Chief Deputy Attorney General|last = |first = |date = 2006-08-12|work = WBOC|accessdate = 2016-01-25|archive-date = 2016-02-02|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160202092038/http://www.wboc.com/story/5788035/gebelein-named-as-delawares-next-chief-deputy-attorney-general|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url = https://www.whitehouse.gov/the-press-office/2011/05/11/president-obama-nominates-three-district-court-bench|title = President Obama Nominates Three for District Court Bench|last = |first = |date = 2011-05-11|work = White House|accessdate = 2016-01-25|quote = Richard G. Andrews is the State Prosecutor for Delaware, a position he has held since 2007.|archive-date = 2016-01-22|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160122001512/https://www.whitehouse.gov/the-press-office/2011/05/11/president-obama-nominates-three-district-court-bench|dead-url = no}}</ref> 2010年11月，博·拜登参选谋求连任，以78.9%的得票率获得压倒性胜利，成功连任特拉华州总检察长一职。<ref name=":7" /> 2014年4月，博·拜登表示将不会继续参选寻求第三个任期，同时表示将在卸任后于2016年参选{{Le|特拉华州州长列表|List of Governors of Delaware|特拉华州州长}}，希望能接替任期将满的民主党籍州长[[杰克·马凯尔|杰克·马凯尔]]。<ref>{{cite news |last=Parra |first=Esteban |title=Denn takes race for Attorney General |url=http://www.delawareonline.com/story/news/politics/2014/11/04/denn-takes-race-attorney-general/18508679/ |accessdate=November 15, 2014 |work=The News Journal |date=November 5, 2014 |archive-date=2018-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180113093420/http://www.delawareonline.com/story/news/politics/2014/11/04/denn-takes-race-attorney-general/18508679/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Beau Biden says he plans to run for governor in Delaware|url=http://politicalticker.blogs.cnn.com/2014/04/17/beau-biden-says-he-plans-to-run-for-governor-in-delaware/?hpt=hp_t2|accessdate=April 17, 2014|publisher=CNN|date=April 17, 2014|archive-date=2016-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160118132828/http://politicalticker.blogs.cnn.com/2014/04/17/beau-biden-says-he-plans-to-run-for-governor-in-delaware/?hpt=hp_t2|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://www.beaubiden.com/splash/ A message from Beau Biden] {{Wayback|url=http://www.beaubiden.com/splash/ |date=20140419025318 }}, ''Beau Biden: Delaware's Attorney General'', Wilmington, DE: Biden for Attorney General, 2014. Retrieved May 7, 2014.</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.delawareonline.com/story/news/politics/2014/04/17/beau-biden-will-seek-rd-ag-term/7819377/|title = Beau Biden to run for governor in 2016|last = Starkey|first = Jonathan|date = 2014-04-18|work = The News Journal|accessdate = 2016-01-25|archive-date = 2021-06-13|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210613082337/https://www.delawareonline.com/story/news/politics/2014/04/17/beau-biden-will-seek-rd-ag-term/7819377/|dead-url = no}}</ref> 

博·拜登在任期间针对性侵犯，尤其是儿童性侵犯作出了一系列努力。他支持并推动立法，加强了对性侵犯者的惩罚，新法要求性犯罪者向警方注册登记的频率更加频繁，对性犯罪者的限制也更多。<ref name="WMDT">{{cite news |title=Lawmakers Endorse Tougher Penalties On Sex Offenders |url=http://www.wmdt.com/topstory/topstory.asp?id=2640 |publisher=WMDT |date=March 29, 2007 |first=Nadia |last=Singh }}{{Dead link|date=2018年7月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=no }}</ref><ref name="APNJ">{{cite news|title = Delaware's enhanced sex offender law starts|url = http://6abc.com/archive/5874960/|agency = [[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|work = The News Journal|date = 2008-01-07|accessdate = 2016-01-25|archive-date = 2016-01-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160118132828/http://6abc.com/archive/5874960/|dead-url = no}}</ref> 2007年，拜登上任第一年就建立了针对儿童性犯罪者的特别工作组“儿童猎手任务组”（{{Lang|en|Child Predator Task Force}}），促成警方和检方的合作，利用最新科技追踪在线猎手以及在线儿童色情交易。<ref name=":8">{{Cite web|url = http://attorneygeneral.delaware.gov/family/childpredatorunit.shtml|title = Child Predator Unit|accessdate = 2016-01-25|author = |date = |publisher = State of Delaware|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151120145733/http://attorneygeneral.delaware.gov/family/childpredatorunit.shtml|archivedate = 2015-11-20}}</ref> 截至2014年，这一小组已经解决了200宗案件，解救了120名遭受侵犯和虐待的儿童。<ref name=":9">{{Cite news|url = http://www.delawareonline.com/story/opinion/contributors/2014/07/26/shining-brighter-light-child-sexual-abuse-delaware/13217015/|title = Shining a brighter light on child sexual abuse in Delaware|last = Biden|first = Beau|date = 2014-06-26|work = The News Journal|accessdate = 2016-01-25|archive-date = 2021-01-21|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210121030327/https://www.delawareonline.com/story/opinion/contributors/2014/07/26/shining-brighter-light-child-sexual-abuse-delaware/13217015/|dead-url = no}}</ref> 他在任内还与[[特拉华州议会|州议会]]合作，加强了儿童保护的相关法案，提高[[兒童色情|儿童色情]]持有者的最低刑罚，对儿童色情持有者和传播者的处罚更加严厉，对在线猎手也增大了惩罚力度。<ref name=":8" /><ref name=":9" /><ref>{{Cite news|url = http://news.delaware.gov/2008/07/18/attorney-general-biden-announces-stronger-child-protection-statutes/|title = Attorney General Biden Announces Stronger Child Protection Statutes|last = |first = |date = 2008-07-18|work = State of Delaware|accessdate = 2016-01-25|archive-date = 2016-03-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160309173006/http://news.delaware.gov/2008/07/18/attorney-general-biden-announces-stronger-child-protection-statutes/|dead-url = no}}</ref> 2013年，博·拜登还建立了“儿童受害人特别组”（{{Lang|en|Child Victims Unit}}），直接关注与儿童死亡和生命威胁相关的案件。<ref name=":9" /> 特拉华州乃至美国历史上最恶劣的儿童性侵罪犯之一，涉嫌对103名儿童实施侵犯的儿科医生{{Le|厄尔·布拉德利|Earl Bradley}}便是在博·拜登任内被起诉，并被判处14个终生监禁加165年徒刑不得假释。<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://abcnews.go.com/WN/delaware-pediatrician-earl-bradley-indicted-103-counts-sexual/story?id=9921990|title = Pediatrician Earl Bradley Charged With Molestation of 103 Children|last = Friedman|first = Emily|date = 2010-02-23|work = ABC News|accessdate = 2016-01-25|archive-date = 2016-01-13|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160113225712/http://abcnews.go.com/WN/delaware-pediatrician-earl-bradley-indicted-103-counts-sexual/story?id=9921990|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2015/06/01/beau-biden-prosecuted-one-of-the-worst-pedophiles-in-american-history/|title = Beau Biden prosecuted one of the worst pedophiles in American history|last = Moyer|first = Justin Wm.|date = 2015-06-01|work = The Washington Post|accessdate = 2016-01-25|archive-date = 2016-01-30|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160130092149/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2015/06/01/beau-biden-prosecuted-one-of-the-worst-pedophiles-in-american-history/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name=":10" />

博·拜登的父亲乔·拜登为参加[[2008年美国总统选举|2008年大选]]而辞去参议员一职后，公众曾一度预计他会参加补选，接替父亲成为特拉华州联邦参议员。<ref>{{cite web|url = http://politicalticker.blogs.cnn.com/2008/11/24/former-biden-advisor-senate-replacement-picked/#more-31280|title = Former Biden advisor picked as Senate replacement|publisher = CNN|accessdate = 2016-01-25|last = Kornreich|first = Lauren|date = 2008-11-24|archive-date = 2016-01-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160125221929/http://politicalticker.blogs.cnn.com/2008/11/24/former-biden-advisor-senate-replacement-picked/#more-31280|dead-url = no}}</ref> 乔·拜登则在一篇声明中提到：“……我相信我的儿子……能成为一个出色的美国联邦参议员，正如我也相信他一直是一位出色的总检察长。……博在踏进政治生涯之时就已经明确表示要靠自己获得自己的成功。如果他决定在未来参选参议员，他将靠自己的能力参选获胜。”<ref>{{cite web|first = Sarah|last = Brumfield|url = http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2008/11/24/ted-kaufman-bidens-replac_n_146103.html|title = Ted Kaufman: Biden's Replacement Picked|work = The Huffington Post|agency = Associated Press|date = 2008-12-25|accessdate = 2016-01-25|archive-date = 2016-01-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160118132828/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2008/11/24/ted-kaufman-bidens-replac_n_146103.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>但2010年1月，厄尔·布拉德利刚被逮捕一个月时，博·拜登表明自己希望能以总检察长的身份专-{注}-解决布拉德利案，因此将不参加参议院补选。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/dcnow/2010/01/beau-biden-takes-a-pass-on-a-senate-run.html | work=Los Angeles Times | title=D.C. Now | date=January 25, 2010 | accessdate=2016-01-25 | archive-date=2010-01-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100128205156/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/dcnow/2010/01/beau-biden-takes-a-pass-on-a-senate-run.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.politico.com/story/2010/01/beau-biden-declines-senate-bid-031952|title = Beau Biden declines Senate bid|last = Mahtesian|first = Charles|date = 2010-01-25|work = Politico|accessdate = 2016-01-25|archive-date = 2016-02-01|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160201152955/http://www.politico.com/story/2010/01/beau-biden-declines-senate-bid-031952|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name=":10">{{Cite news|url = http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3105948/The-sick-pedophile-pediatrician-Beau-Biden-prosecuted-run-Senate.html|title = How Beau Biden made it his mission to prosecute a sick pedophile pediatrician rather than run for the Senate|last = |first = |date = 2015-06-01|work = Daily Mail|accessdate = 2016-01-25|archive-date = 2016-03-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304115513/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3105948/The-sick-pedophile-pediatrician-Beau-Biden-prosecuted-run-Senate.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>

