== 患病逝世和纪念 ==
[[File:Beau_biden_funeral_wilminton.jpeg|thumb]]和[[吉尔·拜登|吉尔·拜登]]触摸棺材告别遗体的瞬间。]]

博·拜登在人生的最后几年一直在与[[脑癌|脑癌]]作斗争。<ref name=":1" /><ref name="Kane">{{cite news|first = Paul|last = Kane|url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/2015/05/30/e1ac5a2a-0731-11e5-a428-c984eb077d4e_story.html|title = Beau Biden, vice president’s son, dies of brain cancer|newspaper = The Washington Post|date = May 30, 2015|accessdate = 2016-01-25|archive-date = 2016-01-21|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160121201053/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/2015/05/30/e1ac5a2a-0731-11e5-a428-c984eb077d4e_story.html|dead-url = no}}</ref> 2010年5月12日，博·拜登因“头痛、肢体麻木和瘫痪”被送往特拉华州[[纽瓦克_(特拉华州)|纽瓦克]]的克里斯蒂安娜医院（{{Lang|en|Christiana Hospital}}）；官方消息称他出现了“轻微中风”。<ref name=":1" /><ref name="Barish">{{cite news|first = Cris|last = Barish|url = http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2013/08/21/beau-biden-awaits-cancer-results/2680405/|title = Beau Biden awaits cancer results|location = Wilmington, Del.|newspaper = |date = 2013-08-21|work = USA Today|accessdate = 2016-01-24|archive-date = 2016-01-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160118132828/http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2013/08/21/beau-biden-awaits-cancer-results/2680405/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2010/05/11/beau-biden-hospitalized-v_n_571514.html|title = Beau Biden Hospitalized After Suffering 'Mild Stroke': Vice President Son Recovering In Delaware Hospital|last = Walters|first = Patrick|date = 2010-11-05|work = [[The_Huffington_Post|The Huffington Post]]|accessdate = 2016-01-24|agency = [[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|archive-date = 2016-02-01|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160201102026/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2010/05/11/beau-biden-hospitalized-v_n_571514.html|dead-url = no}}</ref> 之后转院至[[费城|费城]]的{{Le|托马斯·杰斐逊大学医院|Thomas Jefferson University Hospital}}留院观察至5月18日，出院后又回到工作岗位。<ref name="Barish" />

2013年8月，博·拜登在长时间的旅程后出现了“虚弱和方向感迷失”的症状，之后辗转[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]和费城的多家医院，最终被[[休斯敦|休斯敦]][[德州大學安德森癌症中心|德州大學安德森癌症中心]]收治，<ref name=":1" /><ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2013/08/19/beau-biden-hospitalized/2675041/|title = Beau Biden hospitalized in Texas, undergoes tests|last = Starkey|first = Jonathan|date = 2013-08-19|work = USA Today|accessdate = 2016-01-24|archive-date = 2013-10-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131025043406/http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2013/08/19/beau-biden-hospitalized/2675041/|dead-url = no}}</ref> 并确诊为脑癌。<ref>{{cite news |first=Lenny |last=Bernstein |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/to-your-health/wp/2015/05/31/brain-cancers-like-beau-bidens-kill-about-15000-adults-each-year/ |title=Brain cancers like Beau Biden’s kill about 15,000 adults each year |newspaper=The Washington Post |date=May 31, 2015 |accessdate=2016-01-25 |archive-date=2015-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151216065331/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/to-your-health/wp/2015/05/31/brain-cancers-like-beau-bidens-kill-about-15000-adults-each-year/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 他接受了手术和常规的放疗、化疗后，一度恢复健康。<ref name="Kane" /><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.foxnews.com/politics/2015/05/31/beau-biden-son-vice-president-joe-biden-dies-brain-cancer/|title=Beau Biden, son of Vice President Joe Biden, dies of brain cancer|author=FoxNews.com|publisher=Fox News Network, LLC|date=May 31, 2015|accessdate=May 31, 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150712001335/http://www.foxnews.com/politics/2015/05/31/beau-biden-son-vice-president-joe-biden-dies-brain-cancer/|archive-date=2015-07-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 2015年春季，博·拜登的脑肿瘤复发，进入[[马里兰州|马里兰州]][[贝塞斯达_(马里兰州)|贝塞斯达]]{{le|沃尔特里德国家军事医疗中心|Walter Reed National Military Medical Center}}治疗，一周后仍宣告不治，于5月30日病逝。<ref name=":1" /><ref name="Kane" /><ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2015/05/19/beau-biden-hospitalized/27607919/|title = Beau Biden, vice president's son, hospitalized|last = Korte|first = Gregory|date = 2015-05-20|work = USA Today|accessdate = 2016-01-24|archive-date = 2015-08-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150823101918/http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2015/05/19/beau-biden-hospitalized/27607919/|dead-url = no}}</ref> 他的逝世在全特拉华州甚至全美造成巨大反响，两党政治人物和民众也纷纷表示悲痛悼念。<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2015/05/31/beau-biden-delaware-mourns-public-servant-patriot/28277985/|title = Beau Biden: Delaware mourns 'public servant, patriot'|last = |first = |date = 2015-06-02|work = USA Today|accessdate = 2016-01-24|archive-date = 2015-12-28|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151228232141/http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2015/05/31/beau-biden-delaware-mourns-public-servant-patriot/28277985/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation-now/2015/05/31/beau-biden-tributes-death-joe-biden/28255365/|title = Beau Biden tributes amass following death|last = Durando|first = Jessica|date = 2015-05-31|work = USA Today|accessdate = 2016-01-24|archive-date = 2015-08-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150823111755/http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation-now/2015/05/31/beau-biden-tributes-death-joe-biden/28255365/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.politico.com/story/2015/06/joe-bidens-tragedy-is-a-death-in-the-american-family-118517|title = In Biden's tragedy, Americans see their own|last = Dovere|first = Edward-Issac|date = 2015-06-01|work = Politico|accessdate = 2016-01-24|archive-date = 2016-02-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160209230651/http://www.politico.com/story/2015/06/joe-bidens-tragedy-is-a-death-in-the-american-family-118517|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/mourners-pay-respects-beau-biden-delaware-n369831|title = Mourners Pay Respects to Beau Biden in Delaware|last = Abdullah|first = Halimah|date = 2015-06-04|work = NBC News|accessdate = 2016-01-24|archive-date = 2016-01-26|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160126070054/http://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/mourners-pay-respects-beau-biden-delaware-n369831|dead-url = no}}</ref> 博·拜登也是自[[约翰·肯尼迪|约翰·肯尼迪]]的幼子[[帕特里克·布维尔·肯尼迪|帕特里克]]于1963年夭折之后首位逝世的在任美国总统或副总统子女。<ref name=":5">{{Cite news|url = http://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2015/jun/06/beau-biden-funeral-joe-biden-obama-clinton|title = Barack Obama delivers tearful eulogy at Beau Biden funeral in Delaware|last = Walters|first = Joanna|date = 2015-06-06|work = [[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|accessdate = 2016-01-24|archive-date = 2016-01-31|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160131130820/http://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2015/jun/06/beau-biden-funeral-joe-biden-obama-clinton|dead-url = no}}</ref>

2015年6月6日，博·拜登的葬礼在他家乡威尔明顿的圣安多尼天主教堂（{{Lang|en|St. Anthony's Roman Catholic Church}}）举行。[[美国总统|美国总统]][[贝拉克·奥巴马|贝拉克·奥巴马]]在家人陪同下出席并致悼词。参加葬礼的还有博·拜登在伊拉克服役期间的[[指挥官|指挥官]][[雷蒙德·奥迪耶诺|雷蒙德·奥迪耶诺]]以及他生前喜爱的歌手[[克里斯·馬丁|克里斯·马丁]]等人。<ref name=":5" /><ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.cnn.com/2015/06/06/politics/beau-biden-hunter-biden-funeral-feat/|title = What we'll remember from Beau Biden's funeral|last = Grinberg|first = Emanuella|date = 2015-06-06|work = CNN|accessdate = 2016-01-24|archive-date = 2016-02-02|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160202190049/http://www.cnn.com/2015/06/06/politics/beau-biden-hunter-biden-funeral-feat/|dead-url = no}}</ref>

博·拜登逝世后，特拉华州为他追授了该州最高的“卓越服务十字勋章”（{{Lang|en|The Conspicuous Service Cross}}）。<ref name=":4">{{cite news |url = http://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/mourners-pay-respects-beau-biden-delaware-n369831|title = Mourners Pay Respect to Beau Biden in Delaware|newspaper = [[NBC_News|NBC News]]|date = June 4, 2015|accessdate = November 20, 2015|deadurl = }}</ref> 而为了感谢拜登任总检察长期间对儿童保护所做的一系列努力，特拉华州创办了以他名字命名的“博·拜登保护儿童基金会”（{{Lang|en|The Beau Biden Foundation for the Protection of Children}}）。基金会成立两天内就收到超过600笔捐款，总额超过12.5万美元。<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.delawareonline.com/story/news/local/2015/06/04/beau-biden-foundation-sees-first-two-days/28496341/|title = Beau Biden foundation sees $125,000 in first two days|last = Parra|first = Esteban|date = 2015-06-04|work = The News Journal|accessdate = 2016-01-25|archive-date = 2021-05-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210509055224/https://www.delawareonline.com/story/news/local/2015/06/04/beau-biden-foundation-sees-first-two-days/28496341/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/06/05/beau-biden-charity_n_7519516.html|title = Beau Biden Charity For Abused Children Raises $125,000 In Two Days|last = |first = |date = 2015-06-04|work = The Huffington Post|accessdate = 2016-01-25|archive-date = 2016-02-01|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160201084010/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/06/05/beau-biden-charity_n_7519516.html|dead-url = no}}</ref> 2015年11月，特拉华州陆军国民警卫队宣布将把位于[[纽卡斯尔_(特拉华州)|纽卡斯尔]]的总部正式更名为“约瑟夫·R·（博）·拜登三世少校武装部队储备中心”（{{Lang|en|Major Joseph R. (Beau) Biden III Armed Forces Reserve Center}}），以示对博·拜登的纪念。<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation-now/2015/11/10/delaware-national-guard-hq-named-beau-biden/75517420/|title = Delaware National Guard HQ to be named for Beau Biden|last = Starkey|first = Jonathan|date = 2015-11-10|work = USA Today|accessdate = 2016-01-24|archive-date = 2015-11-14|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151114072005/http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation-now/2015/11/10/delaware-national-guard-hq-named-beau-biden/75517420/|dead-url = no}}</ref>

乔·拜登於[[2020年美国总统选举|2020年大选]]中当选为美国总统。11月7日选举当晚，拜登發表勝選演說并在現場施放煙火慶祝。拜登团队还在现场播放了博·拜登生前最喜爱的[[酷玩樂團|酷玩樂團]]的歌曲《繁星》（A Sky Full of Stars）作为对儿子的纪念。次日上午，拜登回到家乡德拉瓦州威明頓住所附近的教堂參加彌撒，祭奠博·拜登。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-11-09/491604 |title=(影) 兒子 我贏了! 過世兒生前鼓勵選總統 拜登當選後到墳前報喜訊 {{!}} 國際 {{!}} 新頭殼 Newtalk |access-date=2020-11-09 |archive-date=2020-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118215823/https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-11-09/491604 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

